fr.pinguet62.jsfring.gui

Class AbstractBean<T extends Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.pinguet62.jsfring.gui.AbstractBean<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of objects to display.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractSelectableBean

    public abstract class AbstractBean<T extends Serializable>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Abstract class used to display results in DataTable.

    Eager and lazy loading can be used simple by calling the corresponding method into xHTML view.

    Serialized Form

      • getLazyDataModel

        public org.primefaces.model.LazyDataModel<T> getLazyDataModel()
        Used for lazy loading.
        <p:dataTable lazy="true" value="#{myBean.lazyDataModel}" ...>

        The pagination is managed by the data model .

        Returns:
        lazyDataModel
        See Also:
        AbstractLazyDataModel.load(int, int, String, org.primefaces.model.SortOrder, java.util.Map)

      • getList

        public Iterable<T> getList()
        Used for eager loading.
        <p:dataTable value="#{myBean.list}" ...>

        Cache: because the DataTable repeatedly calls this method, the value is stored on attribute to avoid multiple call in database.
        The value is initialized at the first call (when is null) and reused by next calls.

        See Also:
        AbstractService.findAll(Predicate)
